d cannot be explained\npurely by false-positive contamination. Our key result is a catalog of\nhigh-confidence comoving pairs of stars in TGAS. We discuss the utility of this\ncatalog for making dynamical inferences about the Galaxy, testing stellar\natmosphere models, and validating chemical abundance measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2016 21:00:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Jun 2017 19:06:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-05"}
