 a ring is consistent\nwith the spectroscopic detection of water ice on Bienor. Nevertheless the other\nexplanations cannot be discarded.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Dec 2016 12:58:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-19"}
